In a large bowl combine pasta, lentils, corn, tomato, green pepper and green onion. In a small jar with a tight fitting lid, combine canola oil, vinegar, tomato juice, sugar, dill, garlic, salt, mustard, paprika and pepper, shake well. Pour half the dressing over salad; toss well. Cover; refrigerate at least 2 hours. Before serving, toss again with remaining dressing. Sprinkle sunflower seeds over top.